---
title: Indonesian-Style Chicken and Stir-Fried Noodles with Fried Eggs and Crispy Shallots
description: These stir-fried noodles are inspired by the popular Indonesian dish "mie goreng." A sweet, savoury sauce coats fresh chow mein noodles, chicken and vibrant veggies, and our crispy shallots and a fried egg make every bite super satisfying!
